data.name: cmdcmdEventMessageInsert.CommandText
data.value: INSERT INTO [EventMessages] ([_EventTypeID], [CreationDate], [MessageBody], [MarketID], [CompanyCode], [ExpiryDate], [_EventMessagesStatusID]) VALUES (@_EventTypeID, @CreationDate, @MessageBody, @MarketID, @CompanyCode, @ExpiryDate, @_EventMessagesStatusID); SELECT EventMessageID, _EventTypeID, CreationDate, MessageBody, MarketID, CompanyCode, ExpiryDate, _EventMessagesStatusID FROM EventMessages WHERE (EventMessageID = SCOPE_IDENTITY())

data.name: cmdEventMessageDelete.CommandText
data.value: DELETE FROM [EventMessages] WHERE (([EventMessageID] = @Original_EventMessageID) AND ([_EventTypeID] = @Original__EventTypeID) AND ((@IsNull_CreationDate = 1 AND [CreationDate] IS NULL) OR ([CreationDate] = @Original_CreationDate)) AND ((@IsNull_MarketID = 1 AND [MarketID] IS NULL) OR ([MarketID] = @Original_MarketID)) AND ((@IsNull_CompanyCode = 1 AND [CompanyCode] IS NULL) OR ([CompanyCode] = @Original_CompanyCode)) AND ((@IsNull_ExpiryDate = 1 AND [ExpiryDate] IS NULL) OR ([ExpiryDate] = @Original_ExpiryDate)) AND ((@IsNull__EventMessagesStatusID = 1 AND [_EventMessagesStatusID] IS NULL) OR ([_EventMessagesStatusID] = @Original__EventMessagesStatusID)))

data.name: cmdGetUserIFANotificationsSelect.CommandText
data.value: SELECT EventIFANotifications.EventIFANotificationID, EventIFANotifications.EventMessageID, EventIFANotifications.EventIFANotificationBody, EventIFANotifications.EventIFANotificationTitle, EventIFANotifications.EventIFASubscriberID, EventIFANotifications.EventIFASubscriberNotificationAddress, EventIFANotifications._EventMessagesStatusID, EventMessages.ParentEventMessageID, EventMessages.FirstParentEventmessageID, EventMessages.ExpiryDate, EventMessages._EventMessagesStatusID AS EventMessageStatus FROM EventIFANotifications INNER JOIN EventMessages ON EventIFANotifications.EventMessageID = EventMessages.EventMessageID WHERE (EventIFANotifications.EventIFASubscriberNotificationAddress = @EventIFASubscriberNotificationAddress) AND (EventMessages.ExpiryDate >= GETDATE() OR EventMessages.ExpiryDate IS NULL)
